reviewText: Truly a classic in gospel lore... genuine praise only the great O'Landa Draper and the Associates could deliver!!!

To me, this is the best performance of OD & TA.  Every song is great.  The choir is wonderful.  Their parts are on point.  The soloists are wonderful.  It is 100% OD & TA- no guest appearances.  A must-have for all gospel music fans.  All the songs, as I said, are great.  Some that stand out are "He's Faithful," "His Blood Washes Me," "I've Gotta Reason," and "Gotta Feelin'."
